content: प्रच्यु {c1c} <ab>A.</ab> {@--1@} To move away, go away, withdraw, retreat. {@--2@} To fall off from, drop down, fall down. {@--3@} To forsake, abandon (as religion). {@--4@} To be ejected or driven, be dislodged, be deprived of, lose (with <ab>abl.</ab>). {@--5@} To flow out, stream forth. {@--6@} To drive, urge on. {%--<ab>Caus.</ab>%} {@--1@} To move, shake. {@--2@} To displace, dislodge, eject, expel. {@--3@} To cause to fall, ruin.
